textfsm_template:
Value ICMP_SEQ (\d+)
Value BYTES (\d+)
Value IP (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)
Value TTL (\d+)
Value TIME (\d+\.\d+)

Start
  ^${BYTES}\s+bytes\s+from\s+${IP}:\s+icmp_seq=${ICMP_SEQ}\s+ttl=${TTL}\s+time=${TIME}\s+ms -> Record

End
